				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-126702/scpoems#post-4540812</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2020 17:58:21 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Crow-Cat</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3952131</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Added two haiku's that I wrote a while ago. I have a third one, but I couldn't come up with a satisfactory third line:</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Open</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Close</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-831">DARK</a> <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-575">DARK</a> <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-1820">DARK</a><br /> Skittering crawling<br /> Under floors, behind closets<br /> Hungry for you</p> </div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
